		<div class="courseListDescription">Students develop a theoretical and practical understanding of binding and finishing processes employed in the graphic communications industry. Students learn about various types of industrial binding and finishing techniques, and equipment required for each. The focus of this course is primarily on the post press processes of folding, stitching and adhesive binding.</div>
	
	
