		<div class="courseListDescription">The number of magazines published these days is greater than ever, but print run lengths are changing with the availability of a range of non-print digital media. This course covers design and current technical specifications and requirements for magazine production and distribution. Students will learn about organizations structures, such as grids, formatting and sequential design. Image capture and manipulation are covered. Students will create and produce a short-run magazine.</div>
	
	
