		<div class="courseListDescription">The book in all its forms remains relevant and permanent. This course covers the strategies, technologies and specifications for modern book design and production. Topics covered include page layout, design, typography and image requirements for books. Appropriate output technologies are explored for various forms of printed books and ebooks. Distribution practices are discussed.</div>
	
	
