		<div class="courseListDescription">Prototyping is an important part in the realization of any kind of package. Starting from the design concept to actual fabrication of the prototype all the necessary steps will be explored. The effect of the material on the actual package as well as the actual shape or form have an influence on the functionality of the package. Sustainability, accessibility and package economics are considered. Students will create prototype packages in the lab component of this course.</div>
	
	
