           <li class="courseListItem" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0 0 10px;list-style-image:none;list-style-type:none;">
           









  
    <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/graphic-communication/GCM/858.html" title="GCM 858 - Advanced Workflows" class="courseListCourseLink"><span class="courseListCourseCode">GCM 858</span> - <span class="courseListCourseName">Advanced Workflows</span></a>
    
	
		<div class="courseListDescription">This advanced course explores in detail current premedia workflow solutions, with a focus on how they can be utilized to their full potential in a modern graphic communications operation. Students will explore advanced features of integrated workflow solutions including detailed file management, customized customer-facing portals, soft proofing, and third-party plug-ins.</div>
	
	
		<div class="courseListLength"><span class="courseInfoLabels">Weekly Contact: </span><span class="courseInfoValues">Lecture: 1 hr. Lab: 2 hrs. </span></div>
	
	
